entry.title: Confirmation Of Approval
entry.content:
It finally happende, I recieved my CoE (Confirmation of Enrolment) from UTS.

This means that I now have an official UTS mail address and login to their intern system. Alongside the CoE, I also recieved a listed of assesed subjects from UTS.

Next step is to get a spot in 24 credits worth of points.

Untill next time!
